    "text": "it support cyclic connections. A propagator network is evaluated as a fixed-point process:\na propagator runs when a cell’s knowledge is _refined_ (i.e. strictly grows), not merely when some message arrives.\n\nThere is no single global evaluation order.\nExecution proceeds by information growth until quiescence (a fixed point)\nis reached.",
